v0.5.0.1 02.06.2007 - r2d22k
-this is mainly a release to fill the SVN for people interested in this project
-added a chatmanager to handle the chat(not yet working, because its not completed), also added several packets
 to handle the chat stuff(GlobalChat, LocalChat, Globalhat_TCP, LocalChatMessage)
-several ingame commands have been implemented(LocalChat), for example a command to zone, have a look into
 the readme for more information
-if try to use a worlditem it will now tell you the ID and the pos, thanks to the LocalChat
-zonemanager class has been added but not implemented yet
-Item class has been added but also not yet implented
-a packet to force zoning(needed for the igcommand to zone) has been added
if something is missing plz tell either me(r2d22k) or MrsNemo

